Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.34,0:02:27.59,op kara,,0000,0000,0000,,Dream of life
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.26,0:01:20.44,op trans,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}The fight doesn't end until I fulfill my dream
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.44,0:01:26.69,op trans,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I wonder how far I've come now?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.69,0:01:31.99,op trans,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}In ten years, I'll be living the dream
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.99,0:01:38.50,op trans,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}It's the scenario I wrote for myself, so I'll have no regrets
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.50,0:01:45.13,op trans,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}But life isn't that easy, and it's full of obstacles
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.13,0:01:51.47,op trans,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}{\fad(0,751)}Still, I swear to myself that I won't ever back down
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.18,0:02:00.19,op trans,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I have a dream that I absolutely want to achieve
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.19,0:02:06.44,op trans,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}So I fuel my passion until I succeed
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.44,0:02:13.20,op trans,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}There will be meetings and partings along the way
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.20,0:02:19.45,op trans,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}But I'll simply believe in my strength that you've taught me
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.45,0:02:25.34,op trans,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}And rise back up again and again and again
