Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.43,0:22:55.77,ed trans,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}In this world, every day is dull and full of nonsense
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.77,0:23:01.36,ed trans,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I cover my ears, trying to mute the noise
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.36,0:23:08.62,ed trans,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Why do people hurt each other?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.08,0:23:19.92,ed trans,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}In the contradictory, overlapping shadows
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.92,0:23:23.93,ed trans,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}on the recesses of my heart, fallen into despair
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.93,0:23:26.51,ed trans,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}While carrying this pain in my chest,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.51,0:23:29.60,ed trans,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}can I really dream of tomorrow?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.60,0:23:36.52,ed trans,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Remembering the rainbow I found after the rain,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.52,0:23:43.15,ed trans,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I close my eyes; come fly with me into my dream
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.15,0:23:46.62,ed trans,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}If I have you, who shines so strong
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.62,0:23:51.95,ed trans,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I can envision an everlasting rainbow
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.95,0:23:59.88,ed trans,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}And even remember the moonlight that lit us the night we met
